@node Changes




	1.0	First internal release. Compiled with SAS/C 6.56


	1.01	Color bug removed, when R=G=B=$ff


	1.02	Speed +20%


	2.0	Graphical interface
		Kick 3.x only


	version 2.2a: 

	->	NASTY BUG removed, that caused PCD to crash sometimes.

		Major improvement of the graphical interface.
		Thanx to Thierry Schmidt (Pumpkin) for ideas.

		Now the second screen moves by itself when you call
		a requester (ie. Load)

		Modified the default output dir to RAM:

		Bug supressed between intuition & gadtools.

		Busy pointer.

		Saves now the thumbnail screen.

		2 gadgets enable you to see the conversion progression.

		No more WIN_SIZE tooltype. The lower Window size is
		automaticely adjusted.

		The thumbnail saving routines supports 2 buffers, in case
		you have enough memory.

		Speeded up the thumbnail creation.

	->	Now support magnifying with the right mouse button.

	->	Routines uses the Kick 3.1 or a graphic card if present.

		Now if the kickstart is < 3.0, PCD don't crash.

		Use intuition koz' gadtools is too slow.

		The Index file name is built with the CD name.

....SooN

Mode informations saved in index
ARexx
....& you ?


@endnode


